## Conventions

- **Project images:** `/static/projects/images/` → reference as `/projects/images/filename.ext`
- **Post images:** `/static/posts/images/` → reference as `/posts/images/filename.ext`
- **Naming format:** `[slug]-[descriptor].[ext]` (e.g. `ot-reservations-before-after.gif`, `262701-tiktok-convenience-dependency.jpg`)
- **Export:** PNG at 2x resolution from design tools; GIF for animations
- **Drafts:** Set `draft: true` until ready to publish
- **Ordering:** Use `params.weight` (lower = higher priority)

